Package org.freezedry.persistence.builders

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NodeBuilder
    Interface for the classes used to generate InfoNodes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractLeafNodeBuilder
    Generates and InfoNode for primitives (int, double, float, long, etc) and their wrappers, and for Strings.
    AbstractNodeBuilder
    Abstract implementation of the NodeBuilder interface.
    AbstractPrimitiveLeafNodeBuilder
    Abstract class that implements the AbstractPrimitiveLeafNodeBuilder.createInfoNode(Object, String) for classes that are leaves in the semantic model, and also primitive types or wrappers.
    ArrayNodeBuilder
    Generates and InfoNode for arrays.
